data.description: The wait is over! Welcome to this breathtaking 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home in the esteemed Colonial Forge community, a masterpiece of design and craftsmanship spanning over 3,000 sq ft of luxurious living space. This architectural marvel has been freshly painted and is turnkey, ready for you to make it your sanctuary.  From the moment you step inside, you’re greeted by an open and airy floor plan that seamlessly blends modern elegance with functional living. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the gourmet kitchen, equipped with double ovens, stainless steel appliances, and sprawling countertops that make it a chef’s dream. The hardwood floors throughout the main level add a touch of warmth and sophistication, leading you to a grand sunroom that bathes the space in natural light.  The living experience is further enhanced by the property’s rare and highly sought-after lower-level 4th bedroom, offering versatility and convenience for guests or as a dedicated home office. Upstairs, the owner’s suite is nothing short of grandiose, boasting a spacious sitting room that promises serenity and privacy. Its large windows invite the beauty of the outdoors in, creating a serene retreat where you can unwind in luxury.  Outside, the spacious backyard awaits, offering ample room for entertainment, relaxation, and personal enjoyment. Coupled with a two-car garage, this home marries functionality with elegance.  Situated in a prime location, this home provides quick access to Quantico and Fort Belvoir military bases, ensuring convenience for those connected to the service. Just minutes away, the vibrant shopping, dining, and entertainment options of Woodbridge, alongside the historic allure of Fredericksburg, offer a diverse lifestyle. The community’s homeowners’ association adds to the appeal with access to a refreshing pool, perfect for those hot summer days.  This property stands as a testament to luxurious living, as spacious and inviting as a single-family home but with the added benefits and convenience of townhouse living. The beautiful, large windows throughout cast a glow over every room, creating a bright and sunny atmosphere that enhances the open floor plan. The attention to detail in every corner of this stunning home ensures that it may very well be the most beautiful townhouse you’ve ever seen.  Don’t miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your forever home. With its blend of modern amenities, prime location, and over 3,000 sq ft of living space, including a grand owner’s suite and a beautifully appointed gourmet kitchen, it’s ready for you to move in and start making memories. Welcome to your dream home in Colonial Forge, where luxury meets convenience and every day feels like a retreat.  ***Check out the 3D virtual tour
